<template><view class="page" v-if="doctor"><view class="doctor"><view class="avatar">{{doctor.name.slice(0,1)}}</view><view><text class="name">{{doctor.name}} · {{doctor.title||'医师'}}</text><text>{{doctor.departmentName}}</text></view></view><text class="label">选择就诊日期</text><scroll-view scroll-x><view class="dates"><view v-for="d in dates" :key="d" class="date" :class="{on:date===d}" @tap="date=d;slot='' "><text>{{week(d)}}</text><b>{{d.slice(5)}}</b></view></view></scroll-view><text class="label">选择就诊时段</text><view class="slots"><view v-for="item in slotOptions" :key="item.name" class="slot" :class="{on:slot===item.name,disabled:item.remaining===0}" @tap="chooseSlot(item.name)"><b>{{item.name}}</b><text class="remaining-text">{{ item.displayText }}</text></view></view><view class="notice">预约成功后请按时到院，当前阶段暂不收取挂号费用。</view><button :loading="submitting" @tap="submit">确认预约</button></view></template>
<script setup lang="ts">import{computed,ref}from'vue';import{onLoad}from'@dcloudio/uni-app';import{createRegistration,getDoctorDetail,getDoctorSchedule}from'@/api/patient';import type{ScheduleAvailability}from'@/api/patient';import{showError}from'@/utils/request';import type{Doctor}from'@/types/api';const doctor=ref<Doctor>(),dates=ref<string[]>([]),slots=ref<('上午'|'下午')[]>([]),availability=ref<ScheduleAvailability[]>([]),date=ref(''),slot=ref(''),submitting=ref(false);const week=(d:string)=>['周日','周一','周二','周三','周四','周五','周六'][new Date(`${d}T00:00:00`).getDay()];const remaining=(s:'上午'|'下午')=>Number(availability.value.find(item=>item.date===date.value&&item.timeSlot===s)?.remaining??0);const slotOptions=computed(()=>slots.value.map(name=>{const count=remaining(name);return{name,remaining:count,displayText:count>0?'余 '+String(count)+' 号':'已约满'}}));const chooseSlot=(s:'上午'|'下午')=>{if(remaining(s)===0)return uni.showToast({title:'该时段已约满',icon:'none'});slot.value=s};onLoad(async q=>{try{const id=Number(q?.doctorId);const schedule=await getDoctorSchedule(id);doctor.value=await getDoctorDetail(id);dates.value=schedule.dates;slots.value=schedule.timeSlots;availability.value=schedule.availability||[];date.value=dates.value[0]||''}catch(e){showError(e)}});async function submit(){if(!date.value||!slot.value)return uni.showToast({title:'请选择日期和时段',icon:'none'});if(!uni.getStorageSync('patient_token'))return uni.showToast({title:'请先在个人中心完成微信登录',icon:'none'});submitting.value=true;try{const r=await createRegistration({doctorId:doctor.value!.id,registrationDate:date.value,timeSlot:slot.value});uni.showToast({title:'预约成功',icon:'success'});setTimeout(()=>uni.redirectTo({url:`/pages/registrations/detail?id=${r.id}`}),800)}catch(e){showError(e)}finally{submitting.value=false}}</script>
<style scoped>.page{padding:30rpx}.doctor{display:flex;align-items:center;background:linear-gradient(145deg,#075f72,#15958e);color:#fff;border-radius:30rpx;padding:30rpx}.avatar{width:96rpx;height:96rpx;border-radius:28rpx;background:rgba(255,255,255,.2);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:36rpx;margin-right:24rpx}.doctor text{display:block;font-size:23rpx;opacity:.8}.doctor .name{font-size:30rpx;font-weight:700;opacity:1;margin-bottom:10rpx}.label{display:block;font-size:29rpx;font-weight:700;margin:42rpx 0 22rpx}.dates{display:flex;gap:16rpx}.date{flex:none;width:124rpx;padding:20rpx 0;text-align:center;border-radius:24rpx;background:#fff;color:#7b8e96}.date text,.date b{display:block}.date b{font-size:27rpx;margin-top:8rpx}.date.on,.slot.on{background:#087f84;color:#fff}.slots{display:flex;gap:20rpx}.slot{flex:1;background:#fff;border-radius:24rpx;padding:28rpx;text-align:center;transition:.2s}.slot b,.slot text{display:block}.slot .remaining-text{font-size:22rpx;font-weight:650}.remaining-row{display:flex;align-items:baseline;justify-content:center;gap:6rpx;margin-top:10rpx;color:#3b9b7b;font-size:20rpx}.remaining-number{font-size:28rpx!important;font-weight:750;color:#16876e!important}.slot.on text,.slot.on .remaining-row{color:#fff!important}.slot.disabled{background:#edf1f2;color:#a9b4b8}.slot.disabled text{color:#a9b4b8}.notice{margin:36rpx 0;padding:24rpx;background:#eaf6f3;color:#4b7975;border-radius:20rpx;font-size:22rpx;line-height:1.6}button{background:#087f84;color:#fff;border-radius:24rpx;font-size:29rpx}</style>
